name: Leandro e Leonardo
description: '''Leandro e Leonardo''' were a Brazilian ''[[Sertanejo music|sertanejo]]'' duo. The two brothers (third and fourth of eight siblings), '''Leandro''' (born '''Luiz José da Costa''', August 15, 1961–June 23, 1998) and '''Leonardo''' (born '''Emival Eterno da Costa''', born July 25, 1963), were from [[Goianápolis]].
